{"tid":742181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老習鳩up句口號，cctvb放頭條重點討論","createTime":"2018-07-14T10:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T11:55:51.000Z","uid":29804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41962b600ba4af403dfd8aaad26834d55447ddbe","tid":742181,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b44a81de6bfc778c5f3928daf7646580ad8e13","tid":742181,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點新聞<br />\n<br />\n雜種指示大力發展芯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6b0be68261e203660dacc668c63c441f6bf754","tid":742181,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"美國正式撤銷對中興通訊的禁令，「中興事件」引發內地思考國產晶片的發展。中共總書記習近平指示，要組建針對性的科創系統，強調關鍵核心技術是「國之重器」。廣州一間晶片公司聲稱有能力打破美國的壟斷。<br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平星期五主持中央財經委員會會議，會議指出，國家的科技發展水平，特別是關鍵核心技術創新能力，與國際先進水平仍有很大差距，要改革重大科技項目的立項及執行方式，培育尖端科學儀器製造企業及人才等，充分利用國際創新資源，開闢多元化合作渠道。<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB <a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b49d0b0e60383a83ba4bdc7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5b49d0b0e60383a83ba4bdc7&d=Id4rIygsUOkloCAncYl3yf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=65677e4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b49d0b0e60383a83ba4bdc7</a>"}]}